2026-04-04  Ryan Musante

	Tagged as v2.20

	* Fact-check corrections verified against upstream sources
	* README.md: §10 Restructure: Replace inline override values
	  and per-tier subtables with single consolidated table; all
	  override key=value pairs now live exclusively in companion
	  config files; README retains tier, core, and notes columns
	* README.md: §10 Tier 3 / 3DS: Update Azahar from "2125.0 at
	  Alpha 4" to stable 2125.0 (released 2026-03-24); core now
	  available via RetroArch core downloader and built-in on
	  iOS/tvOS; fix core option keys from mixed citra_/azahar_
	  prefix to azahar_ prefix (stable 2125.0 keys)
	* README.md: §5 BIOS table: Nintendo DS changed from
	  Required: Yes to Optional; add note that melonDS DS includes
	  built-in HLE BIOS replacements (native BIOS required only
	  for firmware boot and GBA Slot-2 connectivity)
	* README.md: §12 Per-core overrides checklist: Replace
	  per-core detail lines with config file upload references
	* config/{Mesen,Snes9x,mGBA,Genesis Plus GX,Beetle PCE Fast,
	  FinalBurn Neo}: Remove redundant preemptive_frames_enable =
	  true; inherited from global retroarch.cfg — overrides should
	  only contain keys that differ from global per libretro docs
	* README.md: Bump version 2.19 → 2.20, rev.18 → rev.19

2026-04-03  Ryan Musante

	Tagged as v2.19

	* Apply optimization audit (11 findings, 3 high / 5 medium / 3 low)
	* Remove config/ per-core override files (maintained separately);
	  README.md: update §2, §10, §12, Files table accordingly
	* README.md: Add §4 Filesystem layout (Apple TV) subsection with
	  directory tree showing tvOS target paths; cross-reference from
	  §2 step 4, §3 Recommended setup, and §10 override instructions
	* retroarch.cfg: Add 4 keys (68 → 72 active):
	  video_threaded = false (explicit; was omitted, crashes #14978),
	  audio_output_rate = 48000 (match HDMI native),
	  audio_resampler_quality = 3 (Normal/Kaiser for Tier 1 headroom),
	  savestate_max_keep = 10 (bound cache on 64 GB model);
	  update header: remove video_threaded from OMITTED list
	* config/Mupen64Plus-Next: Add preemptive_frames_enable = false
	  (cached_interpreter without JIT; matches PS1 rationale);
	  add core options: FrameDuping = True, EnableLODEmulation = False
	* config/PCSX-ReARMed: Add core option pcsx_rearmed_async_cd
	* config/melonDS DS: Add core option melonds_ds_screen_layout
	* config/Mesen, config/Snes9x: Add video_scale_integer_scaling
	  = 1 (overscale; fills more screen area for 224p content at 4K)
	* config/{Mesen,Snes9x,mGBA,Genesis Plus GX,Beetle PCE Fast}:
	  Add rewind_enable = false (defense-in-depth; FBNeo already had it)
	* README.md: Update §7 video_threaded row (Omitted → OFF);
	  add 4 rows to Additional settings table; update §10 Tier 1
	  and Tier 2 override tables; fix override upload path
	  (Config/config/ → root-level config/); update §2 Installation
	  step 4; update §11 Known Issues #8 workaround; update §12
	  Setup Checklist; update Files table
	* README.md: Bump version 2.18 → 2.19, rev.17 → rev.18

